ushing]] ('''k'''), Lt Samuel Canby ('''w'''), Lt Joseph S. Milne ('''k'''), Sgt [[Frederick F\u00fcger]]\n|}\n\n===[[III Corps (Union Army)|III Corps]]===\nMG [[Daniel Sickles|Daniel E. Sickles]] ('''w''')\n<br>\nMG [[David B. Birney]] ('''w''')\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! style=\"width:25%;\"|Division\n! style=\"width:25%;\"|Brigade\n! Regiments and Others\n|-\n| rowspan=3 |\nFirst Division\n\n<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\nMG [[David B. Birney]]\n<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\nBG [[John Henry Hobart Ward|J. H. Hobart Ward]] ('''w''')\n| 1st Brigade\n<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;\nBG [[Charles K. Graham]] ('''w&c''')\n<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;\nCol Andrew H. Tippin <ref>[http://ebooks.library.cornell.edu/cgi/t/text/pageviewer-idx?c=moawar;cc=moawar;idno=waro0043;node=waro0043%3A8;frm=frameset;view=image;seq=519;page=root;size=100 relieved on July 3]</ref>\n<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;\nCol Henry J. Madill\n|\n* [[57th Pennsylvania Infantry|57th Pennsylvania]] (8 companies): Col Peter Sides ('''w''', July 2), Maj William B. Neeper ('''w&c'''), Cpt Alanson H. Nelson ('''w''')\n* [[63rd Pennsylvania Infantry|63rd Pennsylvania]]: Maj John A. Danks\n* [[68th Pennsylvania Infantry|68th Pennsylvania]]: Col Andrew H. Tippin, Ltc Anthony H. Reynolds ('''w'''), Maj [[Robert E. Winslow (general)|Robert E. Winslow]] ('''w'''), Cpt Milton S. Davis\n* [[105th Pennsylvania Infantry|105th Pennsylvania]]: Col Calvin A. Craig\n* [[114th Pennsylvania Infantry|114th Pennsylvania]]: Ltc Frederick F. Cavada ('''c'''), Cpt Edward R. Bowen <ref>[http://ebooks.library.cornell.edu/cgi/t/text/pageviewer-idx?c=moawar;cc=moawar;idno=waro0043;node=waro0043%3A8;frm=frameset;view=image;seq=523;page=root;size=100 also commanded 141st Pennsylvania]</ref>\n* [[141st Pennsylvania Infantry|141st Pennsylvania]]: Col Henry J. Madill, Maj Israel P. Spaulding  ('''mw&c''')\n|-\n| 2nd Brigade\n<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;\nBG [[John Henry Hobart Ward|J. H. Hobart Ward]]\n<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;\nCol [[Hiram Berdan]]\n|\n* [[20th Regiment Indiana Infantry|2